1
00:00:00,938 --> 00:00:03,838
As compensation for what happened on the Bell Tree Express,

2
00:00:03,838 --> 00:00:07,338
Sonoko invited us to go to Izu Highlands.

3
00:00:08,538 --> 00:00:11,538
