4
00:00:11,538 --> 00:00:14,238
as a tennis coach.

5
00:00:15,938 --> 00:00:17,438
Conan!

6
00:00:17,438 --> 00:00:19,038
By some queer work of fate,

7
00:00:19,038 --> 00:00:20,538
we ended up taking a rest at a villa

8
00:00:20,538 --> 00:00:22,638
where a group of tennis club members were gathered.

9
00:00:22,638 --> 00:00:25,038
