10
00:00:25,038 --> 00:00:27,438
was a corpse in an unnatural position.

11
00:00:30,038 --> 00:00:31,838
Aiming for a 100% solution.

12
00:00:31,838 --> 00:00:34,238
He cleared all mysteries and codes.

13
00:00:34,238 --> 00:00:36,338
I deduced the locked room murder with Bourbon?

14
00:00:36,338 --> 00:00:38,438
What's he after sticking around me?

15
00:00:38,438 --> 00:00:40,038
