66
00:04:30,874 --> 00:04:32,674
after he went skiing.

67
00:04:32,674 --> 00:04:36,674
Back then, the snow behind the lodge lay as high as 2 meters.

68
00:04:37,474 --> 00:04:39,874
He took Ishiguri's joke saying that

69
00:04:39,874 --> 00:04:42,074
jumping from the second floor into it wouldn't kill him literally.

70
00:04:42,074 --> 00:04:44,274
He actually jumped into it.

71
